\N<Girl>Mother, a messenger has arrived. They say it's for your
duties.
\N<Princess Consort Suia>...I understand. I will head there immediately.
\N<Girl>Um, mother... what are these duties about?

\N<Princess Consort Suia>It's too early for you to know that. Don't worry, the time
will come when you must be informed.

\N<Princess Consort Suia>About my role... and the position you are in, as well as
about your brother.
\N<Girl>My... brother...
op_スーイアセノ04u
\N<Princess Consort Suia>Ah, ahh... haah...!
op_スーイアセノ04uu
\N<Seno>Mm... fu... haah...!
op_スーイアセノ04a
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Haah... haah...! Princess Consort...!

\N<Princess Consort Suia>No... it's no good... I can't take any more...! I-I'll break
if we continue...!
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>But... it's my turn next! Please, at least until then...!
\N<Seno>Hey...! Didn't I tell you not to overdo it...!?

\N<Seno>If you're that eager, I'll take care of you...! Just wait
your turn quietly!
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Vice-Captain... ah... both of you are so beautiful...

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>We are truly fortunate...! To be able to experience this, it
was good to surrender to Ryuda!
\N<Seno>Ku...! Don't say such pathetic things...!
op_スーイアセノ04b

\N<Zuuteruka>Yo, you're all fired up today too, huh? Is it that good?
With these two ladies?
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Zuuteruka...?

\N<Zuuteruka>Yeah, keep going. But don't push them too hard, alright?
They're precious bodies after all.
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Of course... I would never be reckless...

\N<Princess Consort Suia>What do you want...!? Isn't it rude to interrupt during
copulation...! Please, leave at once...!

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, I know it's impolite. But I'm concerned about the
baby inside you, making sure these guys aren't being too
rough with you.

\N<Zuuteruka>After all, these guys have something like a yearning for the
old days with you two, right?
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Haah...! Haah...!

\N<Seno>If that's the case, what about it...!? Why would you care
about our bodies, what kind of joke is that!?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, well there's that. After all, you two have been
assigned an important mission.
op_スーイアセノ04c
\N<Princess Consort Suia>A mission... you say?

\N<Zuuteruka>Yeah, a joint operation with me. We're heading to the
frontier ruins city of Myibe together.
\N<Princess Consort Suia>Myibe... why must we go to such a remote place...?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, didn't the late Princess Consort's husband... in
other words, His Grace the Grand Duke have an old connection
with Myibe?

\N<Zuuteruka>You never say anything, do you? It's stingy. Even though
we've been so intimate?

\N<Princess Consort Suia>Why must I speak of such things to you...!? I owe you no
such obligation...!

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... is that so. Well, I'm looking forward to it. In
various ways, huh?
\N<Princess Consort Suia>...

\N<Seno>Hmph... is that okay with you? If we leave this garrison,
don't you think Princess Consort and I might just run
away...!?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... then try running away. Of course, I won't
guarantee the safety of your children left here.

\N<Zuuteruka>After all, who knows whose kids they are? There's no
obligation to protect them, right?
\N<Princess Consort Suia>Wh-what did you say...!?

\N<Zuuteruka>Besides... you won't run away. Where would you go if you
did?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... it's an important mission in a new land. Prepare
yourself mentally and physically. Both your body and your
heart.
\N<Segi>Eh...?
\N<Segi>W-wait a minute, this means...

\N<Segi>...as I thought, the dates noted are close. This means...
right before the day Zuuteruka came to this town...?
\N<Zuuteruka>Well then... Where shall we start our patrol today?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... You two are quite spirited today as well.

\N<Zuuteruka>Even so... those two are more than enough to boost the
morale of Ryuda's troops.

\N<Zuuteruka>No matter how noble the ideals you preach, in the end, a
man's vigor can rise or fall depending on a woman...

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Haah! Haa...!
op_スーイアセノ02u

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Vice-Captain... I... I'm being sent to the battlefield
tomorrow. By the orders of the Ryuda faction... to a harsh
battlefield with no dreams or hope...

\N<Seno>Is that so... That's tough... But listen, okay? Make sure
you come back safely...? I'll be here praying for your safe
return...
op_スーイアセノ02a
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Vi-Vice-Captain...!
\N<Seno>Ahn... It's okay... It feels good...
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Haah! Haa...!

\N<Seno>I'm sorry, you guys. Because I've become like this, I can't
do anything too reckless.

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>No... No matter what form you take, you are an attractive
woman...

\N<Seno>Fu, fufu... Even if it's a lie, it makes me happy. To think
you'd say that to an older woman like me.

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>It's true! I've admired the Vice-Captain since my days in
the national militia!

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>But... why are you doing so much for us? I heard that Her
Highness the Princess Consort doesn't associate with us
former 'Dawn's Ear' soldiers...

\N<Seno>Is that so... But that can't be helped. The Princess Consort
must have her reasons...

\N<Seno>But... I'm different. I'm happy to keep you guys company? So
come on... give me more...
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Vi-Vice-Captain...!
op_スーイアセノ02b
\N<Seno>Ah, ahn!?
op_スーイアセノ02c

\N<Seno>Fufu... That's not good, you know? A woman's body needs to
be treated more gently? My husband, despite his rough
appearance, was quite the gentleman at night.
\N<Former Duchy Soldier>The Captain was...
op_スーイアセノ02d

\N<Seno>Mmm... If only we had a little more power... you guys
wouldn't have to go through this.

\N<Seno>Our weakness is what took away your precious homeland and
place to belong. So... that's why, if I can comfort you with
this body, then that's what I want to do.

\N<Seno>Right now, this is all I have... It's not much, but please
forgive me...

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>What are you saying... It's more than enough! I am
completely satisfied...!

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>While I entrust myself to this soft skin... I can almost
forget about the country and Ryuda...

\N<Seno>Fufu... If you say that, then it makes me feel like there's
meaning in my own survival, even at the cost of sacrificing
my husband.

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>Vice-Captain...! Please don't bear it all alone...! We will
continue to comfort you from now on...!
\N<Seno>...Fufu...

\N<Former Duchy Soldier>When the dawn comes... if... when your child is safely
born... next time... our children will...
\N<Seno>...Yeah. When that time comes... right.
